  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized controlled trial will assess the effect of adding intensive physical activity
      counseling to an outpatient pulmonary rehabilitation program. Counseling including real-time
      feedback on daily activities from an activity monitor will be offered to improve
      participation in physical activities in daily life during and after an outpatient pulmonary
      rehabilitation program.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
